title: CAKE Burnout Rewards! (New usecase/investment to lower the circulating supply)
body:
Cake Burnout.

cost example 100 cake.

50 cake gets instantly burned.

50 cake gets redistributed to prior burnout users and can be claimed.
with this CAKE investors gets a "Life-time" investment in cake that never stops producing cake as long as people burn.

this numbers are an example and could be anything.


this would lock up and burn more cake wich would be a good longterm strategy.
